;THE CONSTRUCT WAS EXPRESSED WITH AN N-TERMINAL PURIFICATION TAG MGSDKIHHHHHHENLYFQG. THE TAG WAS REMOVED WITH TEV PROTEASE LEAVING ONLY A GLYCINE (0) FOLLOWED BY RESIDUES 33-117 OF THE TARGET SEQUENCE. ANALYSIS OF THE PURIFIED PROTEIN BY MASS SPECTROMETRY AND GEL ELECTROPHORESIS SHOWS THAT WHILE THE MAJORITY OF THE PROTEIN WAS CLEAVED, THERE WAS SOME UNCLEAVED PROTEIN PRESENT. SINCE ELECTRON DENSITY WAS OBSERVED FOR RESIDUES -2 AND -1 IN BOTH CHAINS, THE TAG SEQUENCE IS INCLUDED IN THE SEQRES RECORDS. THE CRYSTAL MAY CONTAIN A MIXTURE OF TAG-ON AND TAG-OFF PROTEIN.
;
